{
  "stem": "11672.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 31.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went from [INAUDIBLE], which was a town where the army located.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I walk 35 kilometer to Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in Stalingrad, is a-- a very big fight.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I saw, one day, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Khrushchev, ?] like a general, general [INAUDIBLE], very close.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Where I stand in the-- I called it the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, in the [INAUDIBLE], like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one day, my officer comes over and said, I-- you, you, you, you, you five soldiers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm the fifth.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm a lucky man.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I take that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, you see, this has a big building, empty.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You have to go there and look where the German located.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And tell us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then the Russian [INAUDIBLE] go, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Said yes, ?] and I went.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He-- I come off the third floor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was an empty building.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I met the other fellow, [INAUDIBLE], a gypsy, a very nice, a sweet boy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hour before, played me the-- the accordion.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And I went with mine four sergeants inside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there's three Russian, one gypsy, and I.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Germans see when-- I and mine sergeants walks in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I feel blood here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there's a little river-- not the Volga.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Volga's a big river-- a little river to the knee.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I feel, if I now go over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm bloody-- bloody You know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Up here.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went over the river.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't remember nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And when I wake up three days later, I'm in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A few weeks later, sent me back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Sent me back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then I remember, in 1943, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] end of 1943, is the Russians start to push out the German.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Not from Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
